        number {
            bindings = <
&none           &none                   &none         &none         &none                                                                                                    &none       &none     &none   &none            &none
&none           &kp UNDERSCORE          &kp D         &kp E         &kp F          &none                                                                       &kp CARET     &kp DOLLAR  &kp HASH  &kp AT  &kp EXCLAMATION  &kp PIPE
