&kp LG(Z)       &kp LG(A)               &select_line  &select_word  &kp BACKSPACE  &kp SPACE  &none  &none  &none  &kp LESS_THAN  &kp GREATER_THAN  &kp EQUAL  &kp ASTERISK  &kp N1      &kp N2    &kp N3  &kp FSLH         &kp RS(G)
